ight juicy stylized low poly graphics. On the verge of cartoonishness and semi-realism.<br></li><li>Advanced vehicle physics. For example, tires behave differently on different surfaces, accidents cause damage to machine components.<br></li><li>Music cassettes! Insert into the car radio and listen to music of various genres.<br></li><li><i>A cat at home that needs to be fed!</i><br></li><li>And it's road trip game, eventually!</li></ul>","developers":["IndieMax"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Racing","id":"9"},{"description":"Simulation","id":"28"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1062960/header.jpg?t=1712584009","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"name":"Under the Sand REDUX - a road trip simulator","package_groups":[{"description":"","display_type":0,"is_recurring_subscription":"false","name":"default","save_text":"","selection_text":"Select a purchase option","subs":[{"can_get_free_license":"0","is_free_license":false,"option_description":"","option_text":"UNDER the SAND - <span class=\"discount_original_price\">$9.99</span> $6.99","packageid":355466,"percent_savings":0,"percent_savings_text":"-30% ","price_in_cents_with_discount":699}],"title":"Buy Under the Sand REDUX - a road trip simulator"}],"packages":[355466],"pc_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS *:</strong> Windows 7 or newer<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> 2.0+ GHz<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 4 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> NVIDIA GeForce 470 GTX or equivalent<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> Version 10<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 2 GB available space<br></li><li><strong>Sound Card:</strong> Integrated Audio</li></ul>"},"platforms":{"linux":false,"mac":false,"windows":true},"price_overview":{"currency":"USD","discount_percent